        "abst": "贝洛伯格机械师—希露瓦全面入门攻略",
        "content": "<p><img src=\"https://upload-bbs.miyoushe.com/upload/2023/04/24/159117584/d7adf3cae7e0e2c09061cfe5376b5461_7751871929852841528.png?x-oss-process=image//resize,s_600/quality,q_80/auto-orient,0/interlace,1/format,png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1067\" height=\"600\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #1e1f20; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, Roboto, 'PingFang SC', miui, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff;\">Hello，开拓者们大家好吖，这里是</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-weight: bolder; color: #1e1f20; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, Roboto, 'PingFang SC', miui, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff;\">初始镜像OriginMirror攻略组</span><span style=\"color: #1e1f20; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, Roboto, 'PingFang SC', miui, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff;\">，今天给大家带来的是贝洛伯格机械师&mdash;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-weight: bolder; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, Roboto, 'PingFang SC', miui, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff; color: #ef5fa8;\">希露瓦</span><span style=\"color: #1e1f20; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, Roboto, 'PingFang SC', miui, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff;\">的全方位攻略，曾经的希露瓦是摇滚乐队的一员，唱歌、吉他、贝斯、打鼓样样不在话下，即使现在而成为了一名机械师，她也总喜欢鼓捣那些乐器。这样一名生性乐观活泼的女孩子在玩家手中又是怎样的呢？让我们来逐步了解吧</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #1e1f20; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, Roboto, 'PingFang SC', miui, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img src=\"https://upload-bbs.miyoushe.com/upload/2023/04/24/159117584/af2e39ade31f1d476897b4128ef7c190_7270638143207093834.png?x-oss-process=image//resize,s_600/quality,q_80/auto-orient,0/interlace,1/format,png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1050\" height=\"600\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; outline: none; cursor: unset; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #1e1f20; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, Roboto, 'PingFang SC', miui, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff;\">光锥<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-weight: bolder;\">【拂晓之前】</span>可以为希露瓦提供<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #ef5fa8;\">高额暴伤加成与增伤加成</span>，对希露瓦输出能力的提升较大。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; outline: none; cursor: unset; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #1e1f20; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, Roboto, 'PingFang SC', miui, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff;\">光锥<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-weight: bolder;\">【别让世界静下来】</span>可以让希露瓦<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #ef5fa8;\">进入战斗立即回复能量</span>且<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #ef5fa8;\">提升终结技造成的伤害</span>，可以加速希露瓦启动。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; outline: none; cursor: unset; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #1e1f20; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, Roboto, 'PingFang SC', miui, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff;\">光锥<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-weight: bolder;\">【银河铁道之夜】</span>可以基于场上敌人数量<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #ef5fa8;\">提升希露瓦的攻击力</span>，当敌人目标被击破时还可以提供<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #ef5fa8;\">增伤加成</span>，虽然效果不是很契合希露瓦但也是不错的选择。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; outline: none; cursor: unset; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #1e1f20; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, Roboto, 'PingFang SC', miui, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff;\">光锥<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-weight: bolder;\">【早餐的仪式感】</span>可以为希露瓦提供<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #ef5fa8;\">稳定增伤</span>，在希露瓦消灭敌人时还可以<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #ef5fa8;\">叠层提升自己的攻击力</span>，可以作为过渡光锥装备。</p>",
